name: Tairyo Inu
description: Introducing, for the first time ever, a token contract with a built in volume bot WITHOUT the need for a node called.. The Volumizer! Tairyo, which means "Massive Volume" has a built in volume bot that will trigger on every sell. These type of game changing tokenomics do not come easy. This mechanism requires 2 contracts to be deployed, the token contract and The Volumizer contract.
